These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different games are played: whist, mah-jongg, go, poker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, cain, game, aristoff
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, d&b, classical, soul
1. the fan of funk is the person playing poker##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
3. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
5. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
6. the fan of soul is on the left of the person playing go##1
7. the fan of d&b is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of soul is between the aristoff-smoker and the person playing whist##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Game         | poker      | whist | mah-jongg | go |
| Cigar   | game | montecristo  | cain   | aristoff    |
| Music-Genre     | funk     | classical    | soul    | d&b      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, july, september
City: berlin, liverpool, paris, rome
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, chef, dressmaker, paramedic
1. the chef is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
4. the security-guard is on the far right##1
5. the paramedic is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in march##2
8. the person traveling to rome is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Birthday         | september | july   | march | december  |
| City   | paris     | berlin | rome  | liverpool |
| Job     | paramedic        | dressmaker  | chef    | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, april, september, october
City: paris, venice, london, berlin
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, rose, bellflower, sunflower
1. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in october##2
2. the person traveling to venice is the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
6. the person traveling to london is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person traveling to paris##2
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | february | april   | october     | september     |
| City   | venice  | berlin | london   | paris  |
| Flower     | sunflower      | rose | bellflower | begonia |

