.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, malaysian, brazilian, japanese
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, august, january, june
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, motorbike, tram
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
2. the malaysian is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
5. the person who's birthday is in june is the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the brazilian is the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | australian  | japanese   | brazilian     | malaysian |
| Birthday   | january  | june      | december        | august     |
| Transport         | motorbike | jet-ski | tram | quad-bike   |

