.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dunhill, tiparillo, aristoff
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, lawyer, doctor
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, february, october
1. the aristoff-smoker is the doctor##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the doctor##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the doctor##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
6. the mechanic is on the far left##1
7. the dunhill-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
9. the architect is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar   | montecristo   | aristoff   | tiparillo | dunhill |
| Job         | mechanic      | doctor | architect      | lawyer |
| Birthday     | may | march        | october       | february  |

