.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, dahlia, marigold, tulip
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, ice-hockey, weightlifting
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, pink, green, blue
1. the person who growsdahlia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who likes lavender is the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
6. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
7. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Flower    | marigold   | tulip      | dahlia       | aconite |
| Sport   | biathlon | weightlifting | ice-hockey     | cycling |
| Color     | blue     | pink  | lavender | green |

