.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, motorbike, subway
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, pakistani, thai, british
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, bolivar, baccarat, oliveros
1. the baccarat-smoker is the brazilian##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is between the british and the old-henry-smoker##2
3. the british is the person driving the train##1
4. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
5. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
6. the british is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
7. the brazilian is the person driving the helicopter##1
8. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Transport      | motorbike   | subway          | train | helicopter        |
| Nationality   | thai     | pakistani | british   | brazilian     |
| Cigar           | old-henry | bolivar         | oliveros         | baccarat |

