.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, sailing, surfing, cricket
City: edinburgh, rome, miami, hannover
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, light-blue, pink, azure
1. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
2. the person traveling to miami is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's sport is surfing##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
7. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
8. the person who's sport is swimming is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming      | surfing       | cricket    |
| City           | rome  | miami  | hannover | edinburgh |
| Color   | azure      | pink | light-blue         | ivory    |

