.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, apple, cabbage, pear
4 different pets are kept: goat, dog, pony, rat
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, woodworking, sudoku, magic-tricks
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
3. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
5. the person eating apple is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
8. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
9. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Food   | apple         | asparagus  | cabbage     | pear         |
| Pet        | rat | dog | goat | pony         |
| Hobby      | woodworking         | sudoku  | hiking   | magic-tricks |

