.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, go, snooker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, water, cola, coffee
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, old-henry, oliveros, ritmeester
 1. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 2. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 4. the person drinking cola is between the person playing billiard and the person playing monopoly##2
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 6. the ritmeester-smoker is the person playing go##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking water is between the person playing snooker and the person playing go##2
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Game   | monopoly  | go    | billiard | snooker    |
| Beverage   | tea | cola | water  | coffee |
| Cigar           | oliveros   | ritmeester    | cain        | old-henry   |

