.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, november, august, july
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, house, salsa, metal
4 different games are played: chess, go, canasta, bridge
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the fan of pop##1
6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the fan of house##1
7. the person playing go is on the left of the fan of house##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday      | april                | july  | november | august   |
| Music-Genre           | metal | house | pop   | salsa |
| Game   | go         | chess     | bridge     | canasta |

