3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsiris##3
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who growsiris##2
6. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday          | september    | february  | november  | october |
| Color   | fuchsia | pink | white | azure |
| Flower   | daisy    | bellflower     | iris    | begonia |

