.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, thrillersy, thriller, superhero
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, blue, white, brown
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, poppy, lily, rose
1. the person who growspoppy is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who likes amber##2
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching thrillersy movies is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
7. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
8. the person who likes white is the person watching mystery movies##1
9. the person who likes brown is between the person who growslily and the person who growsamaryllis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre      | mystery | thriller      | thrillersy  | superhero    |
| Color   | white   | blue | brown | amber |
| Flower           | rose      | lily       | poppy   | amaryllis      |

