.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, amber, brown, yellow
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, davidoff, bluemaster
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, chess, domino
1. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes amber is between the person who likes yellow and the person playing mah-jongg##2
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person playing mah-jongg and the baccarat-smoker##2
7. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
8. the swisher-smoker is in an even position##4
9. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | grey    | brown | amber  | yellow  |
| Cigar   | davidoff | swisher       | bluemaster | baccarat |
| Game         | chess   | mah-jongg      | domino | billiard       |

