.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, handball, cycling, snowboarding
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, photography, camping, board-games
House: modern, victorian, townhouse, tower
1. the victorian house is in an even position##4
2. the victorian house is the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the victorian house##1
7. the modern house is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
8. the tower house is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Sport      | cycling      | handball | rugby     | snowboarding    |
| Hobby   | board-games | skydiving      | photography | camping |
| House           | townhouse   | victorian  | modern     | tower |

