There 4 different types of food: apricot, pear, raspberry, kiwi
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, domino, snooker
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
2. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4
3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
4. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person playing poker and the person eating raspberry##2
6. the person playing backgammon is the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
8. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | family    | thriller     | romance    | drama        |
| Food       | raspberry   | apricot | pear | kiwi |
| Game   | snooker | domino      | poker    | backgammon   |

