.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
City: venice, hamburg, prague, london
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, punk, funk, blues
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, fanta, 7up
1. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking water is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person traveling to london##2
3. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to london is the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| City          | hamburg | london  | venice   | prague    |
| Music-Genre   | house  | funk     | blues | punk |
| Beverage   | fanta   | 7up | water | iced-tea   |

