1. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who likes chestnut##1
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
7. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Pet   | turtle | hedgehog | guinea-pig | goldfish   |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | rugby   | parkour     | skiing    |
| Color   | lilac  | ebony | chestnut  | orange |

