6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Birthday    | july    | october    | january  | february |
